Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:46.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you write your name on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:51.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do something at the closed-down school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a courage test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't gather a certain number of people, we can't get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, could you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Sasada's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:16.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying it's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:24.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't think our haughty class rep would be organizing a ghost hunt, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you when everything has gone through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:32.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So they really can't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he in a rush so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that, just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not chasing after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Natsume Reiko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Reiko is my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She already passed aw-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll gobble you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:36.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not something to be used by a low-level Ayakashi like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:42.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have a deal with him to receive the Book of Friends once he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's already been promised to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, be good and get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,should get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost. You don't know who you're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank me with Nanatsuji steamed buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took a liking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:19.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Book of Friends, there are two types of Youkai that come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:25.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The first type is like the one just now, those who are after the Book of Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to control the Youkai whose names are written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other type is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who come back to have their names returned from the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I could eat those steamed buns forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you returned another name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends is getting thinner and thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I return their names, I become very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:06.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many will be left once I inherit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just eat this kid right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you, you damned, cheating fortune cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san is cheerful and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeru-san doesn't talk much, but he's always gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to cause these people trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm causing them utter trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't like leftovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe these'll do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right. It's quite the gourmand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:05:59.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a tooth-mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. It has a special flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I kind of burned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono, I'd like you to return my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:25.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Now that I've had a good look, aren't you the old Dew God?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's grown quite small, so I couldn't tell at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know! You're Madara, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your silly na-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! I'll swallow you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's begin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One who would protect me, show your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:58.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's stuck to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, they're completely stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:07.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a grain of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A grain of rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko was a really sloppy gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably playing with it while she was eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force it apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin feels all tingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If their names get torn apart, so will their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you burn it, they'll turn to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Dew God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:39.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how it is, so please give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun! The bath is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't return your name if I can't take them apart, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do something about it, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Return my name! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's impossible is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:03.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dew God lives in the Seven Forests, right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I brought it because you told me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but what is it used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:22.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precaution. Just put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't bruised, please have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat it all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll keep it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:56.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:07.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say more thoughtful things at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being a poor speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That old lady doesn't have much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't give off much of a delicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dew God's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the weird face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dew God is a real god? And not just a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You came, Natsume-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I was rude to him last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll curse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And Reiko-san, why'd you do something that'll get you cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:49.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in a panic because he believes you're a real god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, Dew God-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm called a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:10:01.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm just a wanderer that settled in this small shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, there was a long drought in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:10.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Distressed by the disaster, the young villagers prayed at this small shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the following day, it happened to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:17.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the villagers would worship the Dew God,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:21.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and would leave many offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:24.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And before I realized it, I was overflowing with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and my form became just as grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I met you, you were as tall as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I barely come up to their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:37.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And just as my body grew because of people's faith in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have diminished in size like this due to the lack of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I offer you a peach, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You met Hana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So her name is Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the sole person to come here and worship me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I return the name stuck to yours, I won't have to force them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, one problem came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the other Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing to Reiko, I was really frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing that the next Ayakashi's name was taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:36.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see him to gloat. {re-edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have forgotten his name, but he was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's drawn quite well if I say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he have any hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:52.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He... didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even one strand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one strand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He happens to live at Sannozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also the god of shadows and moves by walking among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of my drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You damned, accursed fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, our Youkai search began at Sannozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:37.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But after spending several days searching for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,we were unable to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you look sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired from all the searching?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Hana-san can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's within breath's reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to pray too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:10.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like I was the only one coming recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that the Dew God was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start worshipping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise you won't laugh, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:36.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that I saw the Dew God once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way back from girls' school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather was just like today's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:47.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pray just as I always do, and when I raised my face,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a leg behind the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised, but I pretended not to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:14:00.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I then saw a person wearing an old man's mask, who was in quite a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,"The weather is great today," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost replied without thinking, "Yes, you're right."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:15.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But I felt that if a human saw him, the Dew God would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:21.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But even now, I think to myself that it would've been better if I had replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dew God is always alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'd be able to handle being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I should at least talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always alone, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:41.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone is lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,is painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleepwalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a nightmare last night, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You were heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You had an opening in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak minds invite spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to lose your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,you should never let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you lose your life quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to get my hands on the Book of Friends fast and be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you sleepwalk, I'll pull out the fur on your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be told that by a Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him, Natsume-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he really was on this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I called for him, but he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have gone too far, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, let's split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:58.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{just cat making sound effect}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:15:59.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:02.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:24.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks nothing like your picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid, it was the spitting image of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's the same is the character!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, use the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reflect the sunlight and blind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasume-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to get food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How about fighting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you beat me, I'll give you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you could eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Susugi, Dew God, I return your names!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Dew God?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't always be bringing offerings, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even get one peach today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,People are cruel and only care for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You should find a better home while you have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you are loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:35.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and once you have loved, you cannot forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you to walk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That Susugi Youkai would walk along the shadows to go to the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:59.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and in exchange for receiving food scraps, he would wash that house's dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:59.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}Note: "Susugi" - to wash
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you looked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, the city is bright even during the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so we might not see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He has friends on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's glad to have cut his ties with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's true, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:21.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some peaches, Dew God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Dew God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You got smaller again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're glowing? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:44.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hana-san has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:47.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hana-san had been sick for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and it took everything she had to come here recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:56.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the last human to have worshipped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, once she dies, I will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll worship you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's impossible, I'll come pray every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my friend, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go with Hana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always done nothing but watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:35.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I feel like I'll be able to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She heard your voice, Dew God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:56.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have been such charming creatures in the past, and even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:10.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?! What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things that'll get you cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:41.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not today, but there may be something tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is a caring heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:52.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you stupid cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "fortune cat" to you, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "meow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you steamed bun thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that bought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:09.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:47.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:50.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ayakashi from the Eight Fields are crying because some human got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means someone who can see Youkai did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:55.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems kind of suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:59.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tanuma Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:07.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,
